726
01:22:35.117 --> 01:22:37.119
[Kraven] <i>But let me
tell you a little something</i>

727
01:22:37.202 --> 01:22:39.329
<i>about your beloved dark father.</i>

728
01:22:41.081 --> 01:22:45.377
<i>He's the one who killed your family.
Not the Lycans.</i>

729
01:22:46.128 --> 01:22:48.213
